{"tid":579993,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[奧斯卡熱身戰] <Emoji大冒險>大熱掃4獎 湯告魯斯奪影帝","createTime":"2018-03-04T06:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T01:11:52.000Z","uid":35504,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eb12a424b6e8123d6f2b8ba2e4ba0801b6900e0f","tid":579993,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"旨在「表揚」荷李活濫拍爛片的金草莓獎（Razzie Awards），每年總會搶在奧斯卡前公布得獎名單，今年亦不例外。東尼里安迪斯（Tony Leondis）執導、「X教授」柏德烈史超域（Patrick Stewart）及名嘴占士高登（James Corden）聲演的動畫《Emoji大冒險》，包辦最爛電影、導演、劇本及幕前拍檔合共4獎，成為最大「贏家」。<br />\n<br />\n金草莓獎由觀眾投票選出賽果，某程度上比奧斯卡更貼近民意。最爛男女主角分別落入第3度提名終於得獎的《盜墓迷城》湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise），以及在喜劇《Boo 2! A Madea Halloween》反串扮女人的黑人男星泰萊派利（Tyler Perry）手上；至於最爛男女配角則是《左兩爸右兩爸》米路吉遜（Mel Gibson），以及《格雷的五十道色戒2》金碧辛嘉（Kim Basinger）。反觀賽前獲得最多、共9項提名的《變形金剛：終極戰士》，結果空手而回，台前幕後終於可以鬆一口氣吧？<br />\n<br />\n「悼念」捲入性騷擾醜聞電影人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面，金草莓獎亦模仿奧斯卡搞悼念環節，但目標卻非已故影星，而是一眾捲入性騷擾醜聞的圈中人包括電影大亨韋斯汀（Harvey Weinstein）、金像影帝奇雲史柏斯（Kevin Spacey）及德斯汀荷夫曼（Dustin Hoffman）等，極盡諷刺之能事，同時反映主辦單位緊貼「#MeToo」等熱門話題的社會觸角。"},{"pid":"5416e7621cfb8589bc6766cebe65667401134288","tid":579993,"uid":6420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"emoji實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6a689d2bb4b446dda4d78504959be50de86f4b","tid":579993,"uid":35504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:14:12.000Z","msg":"得獎名單<br />\nWorst picture The Emoji Movie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWorst actress Tyler Perry, Boo 2! A Madea Halloween<br />\n<br />\nWorst actor Tom Cruise, The Mummy<br />\n<br />\nWorst supporting actor Mel Gibson, Daddy&rsquo;s Home 2<br />\n<br />\nWorst supporting actress Kim Basinger, Fifty Shades Darker<br />\n<br />\nWorst screen combo Any two obnoxious emojis, The Emoji Movie <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWorst remake, ripoff or sequel Fifty Shades Darker<br />\n<br />\nWorst director Tony Leondis, The Emoji Movie<br />\n<br />\nWorst screenplay The Emoji Movie<br />\n<br />\nSpecial Rotten Tomatoes Award: The Razzie Nominee So Bad You Loved It!: Baywatch<br />\n<br />\nBarry L. Bumstead Award: CHiPs<br />\n<br />\nThe Razzie Redeemer Award<br />\n&quot;A Safe Hollywood-Haven where talent is protected, nourished and allowed to flourish with proper compensation.&quot;"},{"pid":"9b4aa5c21eaa39ad9e4efdd8665d8cb25c4f12a3","tid":579993,"uid":4260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"「悼念」捲入性騷擾醜聞電影人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de2c6c420f61ad81f2d69853c22053ebce67b6a","tid":579993,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「悼念」捲入性騷擾醜聞電影人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs1.mingpao.com/education/20180304/s00020/42aac9d8dd22ff2c0d9532e975a2d859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.mingpao.com%2Feducation%2F20180304%2Fs00020%2F42aac9d8dd22ff2c0d9532e975a2d859.jpg&h=ab08aecd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e432cda0e612459436bc5ae5e029894331595fb","tid":579993,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T10:58:23.000Z","msg":"變型金剛居然無獎"},{"pid":"563b5051335edcf0918519fd52bf3b134d33d23b","tid":579993,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91644a8740c39667d635ac0feac55fcc35